Thats an awesome idea. imagine though its streaming live across cables
throughout the states. The possibility of the audio being further
influenced is greater Im sure. Reminds me of when a radio show was
being done on evps people recording the show played it back later to
listen again and heard messages to them during the play back and this
was being reported from tons of people. So its pretty interesting if
you can actually have this done, cant wait to see what happens.



